The ourgs are a near-extinct race of gigantic ogre-like creatures, one of the most powerful races bred by the god Bandos. They were believed to be extinct, until the God Wars Dungeon thawed out. There, in the Bandos Stronghold, resides General Graardor, the last living ourg.

Players can find ourg bones in the Zogre coffins, after the completion of Zogre Flesh Eaters.

The '''ourgs''' are a near-extinct race of gigantic [[ogre]]-like creatures, one of the most powerful races bred by the god [[Bandos]]. They were believed to be extinct, until the God Wars Dungeon thawed out. There, in the Bandos Stronghold, resides [[General Graardor]], the last living ourg.

Players can find [[ourg bones]] in the Zogre coffins, after the completion of [[Zogre Flesh Eaters]].
